Print a current file input.

# Note

- This macro does not need FIN permission.
- Default behaviour is to print relative path

# Arguments

- a_absolute : Whether to print an input path as absolute.

# Demo

```
% INPUT = /home/user/test
$input()
$input(false)
$input(true)
===
test
test
/home/user/test
```

# Example

$assert($input(),test)
$assert($input(true),/home/user/dir/test)
